        <abstract> 
<p>Offers CD same payment for the 3d issue of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> as for 2d.</p> 
            <p>Has bespoke four better drawings of birds in case a 4th issue is needed.</p> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Vanity Fair</hi> wants CD’s portrait by Carlo Pellegrini ["Ape"].</p> 
